title: Mentally Challenged Andhra Woman Gang-Raped; Row After Chandrababu Naidu Visit - NDTV
content: Mentally Challenged Andhra Woman Gang-Raped; Row After Chandrababu Naidu Visit  NDTVView Full coverage on Google News
description: An alleged case of gang-rape led to political acrimony between the ruling YSR Congress and the Telugu Desam Party in Andhra Pradesh on Friday even as Chief Minister Y S Jagan Mohan Reddy announced an assistance of Rs 10 lakh to the survivor.
